WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
agent-exporter is an archive and governance workbench for AI agent transcripts.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Start with the CLI quickstart. Prove the command surface before anything else.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.000
Export one HTML transcript receipt you can read and keep locally.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Publish the archive shell to organize transcripts, reports, and evidence on one desk.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
This is a local workbench, not a hosted platform or remote runtime.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Governance is a companion lane. It does not replace the transcript-first front door.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
The flagship public packet is still GitHub repo, CLI quickstart, and archive shell proof.
